# Extension Version Bump

- After making any code/content change in this repository, update `manifest.json` version in the same task.
- Use semantic version patch increments by default (for example `1.3.6` -> `1.3.7`) unless the user requests minor/major bump.
- Keep version bump in the same change set so the extension can be reloaded with a new version immediately.
